snippet.title: Dystopia: Contest of Heroes: New Strategy Mobile Game Cinematic Trailer feat. Conor McGregor 2020
snippet.description:
Join Conor McGregor in the world's biggest multiplayer tournament platform and win epic in-game and real-life prizes! Download Dystopia: Contest of Heroes now: https://onelink.to/dystopia

Join hundreds of thousands of other players in competing for awesome prizes in global multiplayer tournaments, establish alliances with other players, and build your empire in the futuristic cyberpunk New York.

Welcome to Dystopia - the future world of cyberpunk! A post-apocalyptic world where the society is being controlled by big corporations. Do you have what it takes to build an empire by taking over districts of New York while collecting sci-fi themed gear, raid other players, and upgrade your base? Develop alliances and lead them into economic growth, support them in raids, or wage wars against other alliances. 

Visit our website for more information: https://dystopia.beetrootlab.com

Music in this video:
Song: Found My Feet
Artist: Jafaris
Album: Stride
